  "full_description": "Chanel Vintage 1984 Medallion Round Pendant Iconic CC Logo Black Leather Triple 3 Strands Layers intertwined Chain Link Chunky Modernist Elegant Necklace Belt, Gold Plated\n\nVery excellent condition. Not any scratches or colour loss. Can be used as necklace too. Versatile belt. Rare to find. 100% Genuine. \n\nIt has a gold tone link chain woven with soft black leather, a triple swag at the front and a Chanel medallions at each end of the swag. Finally it has a large medallion with a cutout CC logo at the end of the chain. Hook fastening and fully adjustable.\n\nSigned and dated on hook. From 1984.\n\nMaterial: 24ct yellow gold plated metal, 100% leather.\n\nSize: 86 *1.0 cm. Pendant: 3.0* 3.0 cm.\n\nWeight: 203 g.\n\n_ _ _\n\nI am a freelancer more than 2 years. I love fashion, I believe jewellery play a very important role in this field. I am really addicted in it, so the related because my full time work. I am very versatile, chasing different kind of jewellery, not matter where they are come from vintage or contemporary.\n\nI collected many vintage jewellery. In the meantime, I am also a costume jewellery designer. I am a new 1stDibs seller, hope you can support my career sincerely. And Hello! Nice to meet you in here.",
